'''热带风暴黛比'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Debby}}）是1994年9月的一个[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]，虽然强度较弱，但却对[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]造成重大损失。系统于9月9日在[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]以东发展成形，是[[1994年大西洋飓风季|1994年大西洋飓风季]]第4个获得命名的风暴。9月10日清晨，黛比[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]，产生暴雨和热带风暴强度阵风。大量降水引发洪灾和[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，岛上约有半数香蕉种植园毁于一旦。因道路和桥梁受损，多个村庄同外界的交通中断。整场风暴一共造成约1.15亿美元（1994年[[美元|美元]]）的损失，邻近的多米尼加也有农作物和水产行业受到打击。

受[[风切变|风切变]]影响，黛比最强烈的[[雷暴|雷暴]]在穿越圣卢西亚期间位于中心以东和以北。[[马提尼克|马提尼克]]的一间气象站测得飓风强度风力，岛上有约2万人失去供电。进入东[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]后，气旋达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]110公里的最高强度，但在风切变的持续影响下仅持续到9月11日便完全消散。[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]有1人因遭遇大浪丧生，风暴还在多米尼加共和国引发停电和洪灾。整场风暴共计夺走9条人命。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Debby 1994 track.png}}
热带风暴黛比源于9月4日离开[[非洲|非洲]]海岸的一股[[东风波|东风波]]。到9月6日时，卫星图像显示行进至非洲和[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]中途海域的东风波已经发展出强烈[[对流|对流]]。受西北向[[风切变|垂直风切变]]影响，对流在次日有显著减少和弱化，直至9月8日风切变消退后才得以重新发展。飓风季结束后的重新分析结果表明，1994年大西洋飓风季的第六号热带低气压是于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月9日中午12点在[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]以东约300公里海域发展形成。<ref name="page1">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim01.gif | title = Tropical Storm Debby Preliminary Report | page = 1 | last = Rappaport | first = Edward | date = 1994-10-17 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-02 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025062234/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim01.gif }}</ref>但[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]实际上要到约24小时后才将其归类<ref name="advis1">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/tropdisc/nal0694.001 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160102140749/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/tropdisc/nal0694.001 | title = Tropical Depression Six Discussion Number One | last = Lawrence | first = Miles | date = 1994-10-10 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-02 | archivedate = 2016-01-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。9月10日清晨，卫星图像显示巴巴多斯以北近海有下层[[大气环流|环流]]存在<ref name="page1" />，美国国家飓风中心也是在这时开始针对系统发布公告<ref name="advis1" />。

热带低气压的组织结构逐渐改善，气象机构为此派[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机前去侦察，结果表明飞行高度行风速约为每小时110公里，中心东北方向还有强烈的[[雨带|雨带]]。侦察机估计地面风速约为每小时93公里，表明低气压已升级成热带风暴黛比。<ref name="page1" />但在风切变的持续影响下，环流中的所有雷暴均已消亡<ref name="advis1" />。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}9月10日凌晨3点，气旋以风力时速105公里强度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]<ref name="page5" />。虽然从卫星图像上看，黛比的结构还较为混乱，但位于[[马提尼克|马提尼克]]的气象站及附近船只所测数据却表明风暴在东[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]有进一步强化，于{{lang|en|UTC}}当天早上6点达到风速每小时110公里的最高强度<ref name="page1" /><ref name="page5">{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Debby Preliminary Report | page = 5 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160102150046/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim05.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim05.gif | deadurl = no | last = Rappaport | first = Edward | date = 1994-10-17 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2012-04-22 | archivedate = 2016-01-02 | format = GIF }}</ref>。不过，美国国家飓风中心在当时的实际操作中估计黛比的风速只达到每小时64公里，110公里的最高风速数据是在风暴过后才获得认可<ref name="advis2">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160102150253/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/tropdisc/nal0694.002 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/tropdisc/nal0694.002 | title = Tropical Storm Debby Discussion Number Two | last = Mayfield | first = Max | date = 1994-10-10 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-02 | archivedate = 2016-01-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气旋继续快速向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动，虽受强烈风切变的不利影响，但风速依然保持强劲<ref name="page1" />。9月12日，飓风猎人未能在系统内发现闭合环流，气象机构因此估计黛比于{{lang|en|UTC}}当天早上6点左右在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]以南洋面消散。风暴残留继续向西移动，于9月15日在墨西哥上空完全消散，只余部分残留云系扩散到[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]内。<ref name="page2">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim02.gif | title = Tropical Storm Debby Preliminary Report | page = 2 | last = Rappaport | first = Edward | date = 1994-10-17 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-02 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | format = GIF | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025062216/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim02.gif }}</ref>

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
美国国家飓风中心发布针对黛比的首份公告时，巴巴多斯、圣卢西亚、[[圣文森特和格林纳丁斯|圣文森特]]和[[多米尼克|多米尼克]]政府相应发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="page7">{{cite report | accessdate = 2016-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160102153126/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim07.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim07.gif | title = Tropical Storm Debby Preliminary Report | page = 5 | last = Rappaport | first = Edward | date = 1994-10-17 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-01-02 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。此外，圣卢西亚气象局早在黛比发展形成之前就已发布洪灾警报<ref name="sl1">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160102160942/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/preloc/stlucia1.gif | author = Saint Lucia Meteorological Service | publisher = National Hurricane Center | title = Report on the 1994 Atlantic hurricane season: Tropical Storm Debby | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-01-02 | accessdate = 2012-04-23 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/preloc/stlucia1.gif | date =  }}</ref>。美国国家飓风中心建议马提尼克发布热带风暴警告，但当地政府实际发布的是暴雨警报<ref name="page4">{{cite report | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim04.gif | page = 4 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160102160834/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim04.gif | title = Tropical Storm Debby Preliminary Report | last = Rappaport | first = Edward | date = 1994-10-17 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-03 | archivedate = 2016-01-02 | format = GIF }}</ref>。气旋首先从巴巴多斯以北经过，岛上因此受到影响，风力约为每小时43公里<ref name="page7" />。圣文森特和巴巴多斯西南部一些房屋的屋顶受轻微损伤，多米尼加及通往北面的多条道路因风暴受损，还出现停电情况<ref name="rw">{{cite web | author = UN Department of Humanitarian Affairs | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 1994-09-13 | title = Caribbean - Tropical Storm Debby Sep 1994 UN DHA Information Report No. 1 | accessdate = 2016-01-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407065459/http://reliefweb.int/report/martinique-france/caribbean-tropical-storm-debby-sep-1994-un-dha-information-report-no-1 | archivedate = 2014-04-07 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/martinique-france/caribbean-tropical-storm-debby-sep-1994-un-dha-information-report-no-1 }}</ref>。多米尼加各地因狂风暴雨导致2800英亩香蕉、143英亩大蕉、355英亩[[块根作物|块根作物]]，还有355英亩树类作物受损，该国农作物和渔业遭受的损失总额估计为3000万[[东加勒比元|东加勒比元]]（相当于1994年的1200万[[美元|美元]]）<ref>{{cite book | author = Charlotte Benson | author2 = Edward Clay | title = Dominica: Natural Disasters and Economic Development of a Small Island State | publisher = World Bank | location = Washington, D.C. | date = 2001-10 | chapter = Annex A | page = 103 | url = http://www.eird.org/esp/cdcapra/pdf/eng/doc14022/doc14022-8.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160102162044/http://www.eird.org/esp/cdcapra/pdf/eng/doc14022/doc14022-8.pdf | deadurl = no | access-date = 2016-01-02 }}</ref>。风暴过后，向风群岛农作物保险公司共计向2189笔索赔要求提供160万东加勒比元（相当于1994年的66万美元）赔偿金<ref name="wincrop">{{cite report | author = Henrica Ferreira | year = 2009 | title = Windward Islands Crop Insurance (1988) Ltd. (WINCROP) | format = PPT | accessdate = 2016-01-03 | archivedate = 2016-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160102164839/http://www.slideserve.com/woods/windward-islands-crop-insurance-1988-ltd-wincrop | url = http://www.slideserve.com/woods/windward-islands-crop-insurance-1988-ltd-wincrop | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。

热带风暴黛比吹袭圣卢西亚期间，[[卡斯特里|卡斯特里]]的维吉耶（{{lang|en|Vigie}}）阵风时速达到74公里<ref name="page7" />，风暴行经该岛期间对沿途造成的破坏最为严重<ref name="page3">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025062227/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim03.gif | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | format = GIF | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/prenhc/prelim03.gif | title = Tropical Storm Debby Preliminary Report | page = 3 | last = Rappaport | first = Edward | date = 1994-10-17 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-02 }}</ref>，全岛大部分地区都受到影响。气旋产生持续超过6小时的暴雨和雷暴，导致多条河流沿线洪水泛滥，低洼地区被淹<ref name="sl1" />。大量降水导致山坡上的房屋被毁<ref name="page3" />，约150人被迫前去避难所暂避<ref name="rw" />。多条公路被冲毁，或是因山体滑坡导致无法通行<ref name="page3" />，还有10座桥梁不是被毁就是严重受创<ref name="sl1" />，导致岛上多个村庄同外界的交通中断<ref name="rw" />。圣雅克桥镇也受到山崩的影响，暴雨还令[[圣卢西亚国际机场|圣卢西亚国际机场]]被51毫米的淤泥覆盖，拉雷伊湾（{{lang|en|Anse La Raye}}）的洪水有齐腰深<ref name="page3" />，该镇居民不得不搭船撤离<ref name="ap1">{{cite news | author = Katherine Hutt | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Baton Rouge Morning Advocate | publisher = National Hurricane Center, leaves trail of heavy damage | series = Tropical Storm Debby: Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | title = Tropical storm kills 3 in Caribbean | accessdate = 2016-01-03 | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160102170508/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/news/brmap1.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/debby/news/brmap1.gif }}</ref>。圣卢西亚约有半数种植园被风暴破坏<ref name="page3" />，许多城镇停水，促使马提尼克和圣文森特政府向各地提供饮用水<ref name="rw" />。圣卢西亚共有4人死亡，24人受伤，所有遇难者都是因两场山体滑坡导致<ref name="page3" />。风暴期间，[[卡斯特里|卡斯特里]]有9名囚犯逃出监狱，报道表明当地还出现趁火打劫的情况<ref name="ap1" />。卡斯特里一间医院的病房因风暴受损，幸而院内人员已经疏散，这所医院之前就有计划重建，黛比的破坏进一步加强了重建的必要性<ref>{{cite report | author = Tony Gibbs | publisher = Consulting Engineers Partnership Ltd. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160103033943/http://www.eird.org/cd/building-codes/pdf/eng/doc10635/doc10635-1.pdf | date = 1996-09-25 | title = Vulnerability Survey of Victoria Hospital: Castries Saint Lucia | location = Barbados | accessdate = 2016-01-03 | url = http://www.eird.org/cd/building-codes/pdf/eng/doc10635/doc10635-1.pdf | page = 1 | format = PDF | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-01-03 }}</ref>。整个圣卢西亚的损失总额估计在2.5亿东加勒比元左右（相当于1994年的约1.03亿美元）<ref name="sl1" />。风暴过后，向风群岛农作物保险公司向该国投保的农作物共计赔偿5802笔，合计金额780万东加勒比元（相当于1994年的320万美元）。截至2008年，热带风暴黛比仍是该公司成立以来造成索赔数额最大的灾难<ref name="wincrop" />。灾后，圣文森特政府开始修复受损建筑和桥梁，向农民提供多样化的农作物，并清理主要河流中的淤泥<ref>{{cite report | title = Government of Saint Lucia Natural Hazard Mitigation Plan | publisher = World Bank | date = 2006-10-27 | page = 26 | accessdate = 2011-10-15 | archivedate = 2011-10-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111015073925/http://stlucia.gov.lc/nemp/plans/HazardMitigationPlan.pdf | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.stlucia.gov.lc/nemp/plans/HazardMitigationPlan.pdf | format = PDF }}</ref>。

气旋途经圣卢西亚期间，位于马提尼克东南部小镇勒沃克兰（{{lang|en|Le Vauclin}}）的一间气象站测得的10分钟[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]为每小时103公里，阵风时速达到156公里，这些数据成为判断黛比最高强度的重要依据<ref name="page2" />。但在风暴活动期间，气象部门及时获知的最高风速是由[[马丁尼克-亚米-凯萨国际机场|马丁尼克-亚米-凯萨国际机场]]测得，10分钟持续风速只有每小时56公里，阵风时速93公里<ref name="page3" />。圣卢西兰约半数区域的降雨量有100毫米，最高的圣约瑟夫（{{lang|en|Saint-Joseph}}）达184毫米<ref name="page2" />。暴雨在岛上各地引发洪灾<ref name="page3" />，泛滥的河水卷走一辆汽车，女车主因此溺毙<ref name="ap1" />。狂风还刮倒部分树木，一些道路受阻，香蕉作物也受到破坏。风暴期间约有2万人失去供电。<ref name="page3" />

热带风暴黛比存在期间，[[美国国家航空航天局|美国国家航空航天局]]曾向风暴发射激光，以测量云层高度，这在历史上尚属首次<ref>{{cite news | date = 1994-09-11 | title = Shuttle Fires Laser Beams at a Tropical Storm | newspaper = New York Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160103045340/http://www.nytimes.com/1994/09/11/us/shuttle-fires-laser-beams-at-a-tropical-storm.html | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1994/09/11/us/shuttle-fires-laser-beams-at-a-tropical-storm.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-01-03 | archivedate = 2016-01-03 }}</ref>。气旋进入加勒比海后，[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]和[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]接获热带风暴警告<ref name="page7" />。波多黎各普遍受狂风吹袭，[[路易斯·穆尼奥斯·马林国际机场|路易斯·穆尼奥斯·马林国际机场]]测得的最高阵风时速为71公里。大风刮倒岛上许多树木，还令多条输电线缆中断，并导致个别房屋及其他建筑物的屋顶受损。汹涌的海浪导致多户沿海民宅进水，[[库莱布拉岛|库莱布拉岛]]的轮渡服务被迫中断。[[卡沃罗霍|卡沃罗霍]]有两个正在海边钓鱼的男子被大浪卷走，最终1死1伤<ref>{{cite journal | volume = 36 | number = 9 | title = Storm Data: A Composite of Outstanding Storms | date = 1994-09 | accessdate = 2016-01-03 | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-A7291C67-BAF0-428C-920D-ED50DAEF99FC.pdf | format = PDF | page = 62 | archivedate = 2016-01-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160103051220/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-A7291C67-BAF0-428C-920D-ED50DAEF99FC.pdf | journal =  }}[http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/IPS/sd/sd.html 此网站] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/IPS/sd/sd.html |date=20160414065723 }}可查询美国国家海洋和大气管理局风暴数据平面出版物的内容，查询结果链接有效时间为24小时，用户可选择“1994-09”获得所需要的信息。</ref>。接下来，多米尼加共和国和[[海地|海地]]南海岸也收到热带风暴警告<ref name="page7" />。黛比消散后，其残留仍然在产生狂风，多米尼加共和国的一间气象站于9月11日测得时速100公里的阵风<ref name="page2" />。风暴还令多条电缆中断，致使数以百计的民居失去供电，还引起3人丧生。该国有多条河流泛滥，一条高速公路被淹<ref name="page3" /><ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Tuscaloosa News | date = 1994-09-11 | title = Debby begins to come apart in Caribbean | accessdate = 2016-01-03 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CEggAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vaUEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3751,3560906&dq=tropical+debby&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-01-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210116023155/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CEggAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vaUEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3751%2C3560906&dq=tropical+debby&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

